<plot>An interview with Actress Linnea Quigley about her experiences on the film, NIGHT OF THE DEMONS. Quigley looks back on her character, co-workers, and the shooting conditions of the film, as well as a few glimpses into her other favorite roles as well. This interview is a feature on the Anchor Bay Entertainment DVD release of NIGHT OF THE DEMONS, which is available in North America (USA &amp; Canada)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?383646</url></doc>
